quran[15{c,v,t}:
112,1,"kaho, woh Allah hai, yaktaa"
112,2,Allah sab se be niaz hai aur sab is ke mohtaaj hain
112,3,nah is ki koi aulaad hai aur nah woh kisi ki aulaad
112,4,aur koi is ka humsar nahi hai
113,1,"kaho, mein panah mangta hon subah ke Rab ki"
113,2,har uss cheez ke shar se jo uss ne peda ki hai
113,3,aur raat ki tareqi ke shar se jab ke woh chhaa jaye
113,4,aur grhon mein phoonknay walon ( ya walion ) ke shar se
113,5,aur haasid ke shar se jab ke woh hasad kere
114,1,"kaho, mein panah mangta hon insanon ke Rab"
114,2,insanon ke badshah
114,3,insanon ke haqeeqi mabood ki
114,4,uss waswasa daalnay walay ke shar se jo baar baar palat kar aata hai
114,5,jo logon ke dilon mein was wasay dalta hai
114,6,khuwa woh jinno mein se ho ya insanon mein se
